Package org.nerd4j.csv.writer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CSVWriteOutcome
    Represents the outcome of a CSV write operation performed by the CSVWriter.write(Object) method.
    CSVWriter<M>
    Represents a CSV destination writer.
    CSVWriterFactory<Model>
    Represents a Factory able to build and configure CSVWriters.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSVWriterFactoryImpl<Model>
    Reference implementation for the CSVWriterFactory interface.
    CSVWriterMetadata<Model>
    Represents the meta-data used to tell a CSVWriterFactoryImpl how to build and configure the related CSVWriters.
    CSVWriterMetadataFactory<Model>
    Represents a Factory able to build CSVWriterMetadata.
